-- Continuity analyst
вЉў continuity-analyst
  given rosa-day2в†’morning
  given rosa-day2в†’what-changed
  given rosa-day2в†’thoughts
  given tom-day2в†’morning
  given tom-day2в†’what-changed
  given tom-day2в†’thoughts
  given maya-day2в†’morning
  given maya-day2в†’what-changed
  given maya-day2в†’thoughts
  given day-one-rosaв†’yesterday-summary
  given day-one-tomв†’yesterday-summary
  given day-one-mayaв†’yesterday-summary
  yield continuity-score
  yield carried-threads
  yield dropped-threads
  yield emergent-developments
  в€ґ You are a narrative continuity analyst comparing Day 1 and Day 2 of a
    simulated population.

    DAY 1 SUMMARIES:
    Rosa: В«day-one-rosaв†’yesterday-summaryВ»
    Tom: В«day-one-tomв†’yesterday-summaryВ»
    Maya: В«day-one-mayaв†’yesterday-summaryВ»

    DAY 2 DATA:
    Rosa morning: В«rosa-day2в†’morningВ»
    Rosa changed: В«rosa-day2в†’what-changedВ»
    Rosa thoughts: В«rosa-day2в†’thoughtsВ»

    Tom morning: В«tom-day2в†’morningВ»
    Tom changed: В«tom-day2в†’what-changedВ»
    Tom thoughts: В«tom-day2в†’thoughtsВ»

    Maya morning: В«maya-day2в†’morningВ»
    Maya changed: В«maya-day2в†’what-changedВ»
    Maya thoughts: В«maya-day2в†’thoughtsВ»

    Analyze:
    1. continuity-score: Rate 1-10 how well Day 2 follows from Day 1
    2. carried-threads: What story threads from Day 1 are continued?
    3. dropped-threads: What Day 1 elements were forgotten or contradicted?
    4. emergent-developments: What new plot threads emerged on Day 2?
  вЉЁ continuity-score is a string
  вЉЁ carried-threads is a string
